{{Vgname|街头小子|ja=アーバンチャンピオン|en=Urban Champion}}是双玩家[[格斗游戏|格斗游戏]]，任天堂制作并于1984年在[[红白机|红白机]]发行。游戏以1984年[[Game_&_Watch|Game & Watch]]游戏《拳击》（又称《拳无虚发》）为灵感<ref name="ignr">{{cite web |author=Lucas M. Thomas |url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/765/765241p1.html |title=Urban Champion - Wii Review at IGN |publisher=Wii.ign.com |date=2007-02-15 |accessdate=2011-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522100412/http://wii.ign.com/articles/765/765241p1.html |archive-date=2011-05-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。这是任天堂的首款2D格斗游戏。游戏在多个平台重制或再版，包括[[任天堂对战系统|任天堂对战系统]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Search: |url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/arcade/569167-vs-urban-champion/data |title=Vs. Urban Champion Release Information for Arcade Games |publisher=GameFAQs |date= |accessdate=2011-02-25 |archive-date=2012-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026065200/http://www.gamefaqs.com/arcade/569167-vs-urban-champion/data |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[任天堂e-Reader|任天堂e-Reader]]、[[Wii|Wii]]和[[WIi_U|WIi U]]的[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]，以及[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]的重制版。

